{"tid":1416653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跟本唔使理林鄭講咩","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:31.000Z","uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f961757e5219a44a9ca146365ad3f866e86a8fe","tid":1416653,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:22:03.000Z","msg":"呢家做既所有野原因只有2個<br />\n<br />\n1. 政府巳經失去誠信，整個管治班子只係識用語言偽術去詭辯，唔係為人民服務，而係為中央服務。<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察等於法律，無人可以問責警署，警察連公安都不如，無枉管。<br />\n<br />\n而若果政府對呢兩個源頭無完全唔處理，示威行動升級係合情合理，就係咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n但都係嗰句，盡量唔好攻擊人，攻擊建築物。<br />\n相反，班狗就唔係，專打人，想殺人。"},{"pid":"8c772df8db0d65ce08a064bc17478378cd442cd4","tid":1416653,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29b378f09309b6dad2140217c72431255cfb01ca","tid":1416653,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ad586acbb8be668d946e3bf2a993a12021dec4cf","tid":1416653,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}